Package: LSS
Type: Package
Title: Latent Semantic Scaling
Date: 2020-03-13
Version: 0.8.4
Authors@R: person("Kohei", "Watanabe", email = "watanabe.kohei@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A word embeddings-based semi-supervised model for document scaling <doi.org/10.1177/0267323117695735>.
    LSS allows users to analyze large and complex corpora on arbitrary dimensions with seed words exploiting efficiency of word embeddings (SVD, Glove).
License: GPL-3
